| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0695 — Recovery Inhibition (coinbasecartel)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c97c313-71c9-5c76-8531-389482cd9d9d"
